    <item>
      <title>法国大选博弈中勒庞的权力之路愈发狭窄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-s-path-to-power-narrows-in-french-game-of-election-chess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在竞争对手采取措施减少三方竞选的数量以利于玛丽娜·勒庞所在的极右翼政党在立法选举的最后一轮中获胜之后，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟在组建法国下一届政府时面临着更大的障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-s-path-to-power-narrows-in-french-game-of-election-chess</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:56:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱在访问巴西前称卢拉为“白痴恐龙”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/milei-calls-lula-an-idiot-dinosaur-ahead-of-brazil-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱称路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦是“愚蠢的恐龙”和共产主义者，这进一步加剧了阿根廷与邻国之间的长期不和。而就在前一天，米莱还选择在卢拉即将访问巴西时拒绝他的到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/milei-calls-lula-an-idiot-dinosaur-ahead-of-brazil-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
